 takes his chance by sitting AFK *anywhere*, and a moron sits AFK at a zone line or other often travelled region. I got a GD mask once from a person who sat down, /camp desktop, and walked away. I happened on him just before he poofed.<br><br>He was sitting at the FV/FM zone, FV side =) He figured hide was good enough, but my shaman had see invis up....<br><br>Either way, I agree, AFK is NOT immunity, it is stupid. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#2f2f4f><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/uceescritdabossalini.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Ceescrit da Bossalini</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/ezgfx/gicons/white_fire.gif" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(2/7/02 10:58:06 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousefrm15.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=584.topic&index=2>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: couple things</span><hr size=1> AFK = A Free Kill on Vallon Zek<br><br><br>(as I'm sure it is on other PvP servers ;p)<br><br> <p><font face=script size=6 color=red><b><i><u>~Ceescrit da  Bossalini</font></i></u><BR><a href=http://www.illuvitae.com><img src="http://www.aztecmfgcorp.com/_private/eq/illuvitae/pics/illuvitae-sig.jpg" border=0></a><br><font color=yellow>-=Commander in Chief=-</font><BR></b></a> Roag of Vallon Zek (PvP Teams)<br>--------------------------------<BR><i>Detroit Roags find you.  Mug you.</i></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#3B3B3B><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/ufricka.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Fricka</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Moderator</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(2/8/02 1:55:54 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousefrm15.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=584.topic&index=3>Reply</a> 