/image.aspx?path=/Asta/fullsize/swedchef.jpg WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: couple things</span><hr size=1> Crimson potions are instadrinkable and dot you for nominal damage over 2mins(?), disease based. Great to keep handy in pvp versus chanters, just remember to slip outta your fungi for one pulse so the dot can break the mez. Dots only break mez if your total (non-buff) regen is negative. <p>--------------------<BR>Asta Khaan <BR>Defiant Shaman, VZ</p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#2f2f4f><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/uulynvindix.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Ulyn Vindix</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(2/11/02 12:40:26 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousefrm15.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=584.topic&index=6>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: couple things</span><hr size=1> AFK on SZ in the same zone as bind point= Oh please, won't you delevel me?  Happened a few times to people that fell asleep.<br><br><br> <p></p><i></i></td></tr></table><table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top"> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousefrm15.showPrevMessage?topicID=584.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousefrm15.showNextMessage?topicID=584.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br><a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousefrm15.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=584.topic&index=6><img src=http://www.thesafehouse.org/images/reply.jpg border=0 alt="Add Reply"></a> </td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"> <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousefrm15.emailToFriend?topicID=584.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/image/email.gif border=0 alt="Email This To a Friend">